{
  "id": "2021-10-18_screen_english",
  "date": "2021-10-18",
  "corner": "screen_english",
  "corner_label": "Screen English",
  "title": "Why can_t you just be grateful",
  "movie": "",
  "duration_sec": 789.35,
  "audio_url": "https://rtyzdyyfahddqshgyjvn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/gmp-audio/2021-10-18_screen_english.mp3",
  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 1.18,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬"
    },
    {
      "start": 1.18,
      "end": 25.37,
      "text": "영화 감상과 영어 공부를 동시에 스크린 잉글리쉬 타임"
    },
    {
      "start": 25.37,
      "end": 27.47,
      "text": "10월에 함께하고 있는 영화는"
    },
    {
      "start": 27.47,
      "end": 29.51,
      "text": "After Wedding in New York"
    },
    {
      "start": 29.51,
      "end": 31.09,
      "text": "After the Wedding"
    },
    {
      "start": 31.09,
      "end": 31.69,
      "text": "입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 32.39,
      "end": 33.27,
      "text": "Hello 입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 33.33,
      "end": 34.73,
      "text": "Happy Monday, Chris."
    },
    {
      "start": 34.85,
      "end": 36.59,
      "text": "Happy Monday, Beautiful Monday."
    },
    {
      "start": 37.59,
      "end": 40.13,
      "text": "다들 이렇게 반가워해 주시면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 40.13,
      "end": 43.79,
      "text": "아주 아름다운 Monday를 시작하고 계실 거라고 생각을 합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 43.91,
      "end": 44.99,
      "text": "Every day is a beautiful day."
    },
    {
      "start": 45.87,
      "end": 48.57,
      "text": "역시 positive한 우리 크쌤 오셨고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 49.09,
      "end": 51.69,
      "text": "Do you remember what Isabel was wearing?"
    },
    {
      "start": 51.69,
      "end": 52.91,
      "text": "When"
    },
    {
      "start": 52.91,
      "end": 54.49,
      "text": "이 영화 내내"
    },
    {
      "start": 54.49,
      "end": 55.47,
      "text": "Throughout the whole gym"
    },
    {
      "start": 55.47,
      "end": 56.69,
      "text": "She wore the same outfit"
    },
    {
      "start": 56.69,
      "end": 57.53,
      "text": "Yeah, that's right."
    },
    {
      "start": 57.55,
      "end": 58.05,
      "text": "For the whole movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 58.05,
      "end": 60.97,
      "text": "I remember she liked comfortable clothes"
    },
    {
      "start": 60.97,
      "end": 61.97,
      "text": "Yeah, it was like"
    },
    {
      "start": 61.97,
      "end": 63.07,
      "text": "Because she's living in India"
    },
    {
      "start": 63.07,
      "end": 63.75,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 63.75,
      "end": 65.33,
      "text": "So some kind of"
    },
    {
      "start": 65.33,
      "end": 67.87,
      "text": "Sort of traditional Indian clothes"
    },
    {
      "start": 67.87,
      "end": 70.03,
      "text": "Yeah, like India 한복"
    },
    {
      "start": 70.03,
      "end": 70.33,
      "text": "Red cape"
    },
    {
      "start": 70.33,
      "end": 71.35,
      "text": "Red cape"
    },
    {
      "start": 71.35,
      "end": 71.79,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 71.79,
      "end": 74.47,
      "text": "약간 빨간 그런 케이프를 두르고"
    },
    {
      "start": 74.47,
      "end": 77.11,
      "text": "항상 다녔던 장면이 기억이 납니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 77.33,
      "end": 78.49,
      "text": "근데 굉장히 뭔가 좀"
    },
    {
      "start": 78.49,
      "end": 79.81,
      "text": "엑소에 어리케 보였고"
    },
    {
      "start": 79.81,
      "end": 81.97,
      "text": "Mysterious한 면도 있었던 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 82.15,
      "end": 82.99,
      "text": "I also remember"
    },
    {
      "start": 82.99,
      "end": 84.47,
      "text": "Her taking her off"
    },
    {
      "start": 84.47,
      "end": 85.73,
      "text": "She took her shoes off"
    },
    {
      "start": 85.73,
      "end": 86.53,
      "text": "A lot"
    },
    {
      "start": 86.53,
      "end": 87.07,
      "text": "Right"
    },
    {
      "start": 87.07,
      "end": 88.95,
      "text": "Especially when she was taking the stairs"
    },
    {
      "start": 88.95,
      "end": 89.99,
      "text": "Right"
    },
    {
      "start": 89.99,
      "end": 91.67,
      "text": "I guess that's traditional in India"
    },
    {
      "start": 91.67,
      "end": 92.77,
      "text": "아, 그런가?"
    },
    {
      "start": 92.85,
      "end": 94.71,
      "text": "Or maybe she didn't even wear shoes"
    },
    {
      "start": 94.71,
      "end": 95.95,
      "text": "At the orphanage"
    },
    {
      "start": 95.95,
      "end": 97.03,
      "text": "Yeah, 맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 97.19,
      "end": 100.61,
      "text": "맨발로 계단을 막 뛰어다니던 장면도 기억이 납니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 100.73,
      "end": 102.29,
      "text": "When she was angry, especially"
    },
    {
      "start": 102.29,
      "end": 102.87,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 102.87,
      "end": 105.21,
      "text": "특히 뉴욕에 와서도 계속해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 105.21,
      "end": 107.97,
      "text": "그런 인도 스타일을 추구했던 모습이"
    },
    {
      "start": 107.97,
      "end": 108.91,
      "text": "인상적이었는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 108.91,
      "end": 109.57,
      "text": "아, 여전하죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 109.73,
      "end": 110.11,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.11,
      "end": 112.29,
      "text": "근데 확실히 compared to Teresa"
    },
    {
      "start": 112.29,
      "end": 114.03,
      "text": "Teresa하고 좀 비교를 해보면"
    },
    {
      "start": 114.03,
      "end": 116.73,
      "text": "이자벨은 확실히 had a different image"
    },
    {
      "start": 116.73,
      "end": 117.51,
      "text": "였던 것 같습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 117.51,
      "end": 118.45,
      "text": "Completely different."
    },
    {
      "start": 118.71,
      "end": 118.77,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 119.19,
      "end": 119.75,
      "text": "Yes"
    },
    {
      "start": 119.75,
      "end": 121.23,
      "text": "She's a businesswoman, right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 121.27,
      "end": 121.61,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 121.61,
      "end": 122.47,
      "text": "Professional"
    },
    {
      "start": 122.47,
      "end": 124.15,
      "text": "응, Teresa는 그랬죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 124.27,
      "end": 125.47,
      "text": "She wears the pants suits"
    },
    {
      "start": 125.47,
      "end": 129.59,
      "text": "항상 정석적인 그런 수트의 의미로"
    },
    {
      "start": 129.59,
      "end": 131.21,
      "text": "그런 옷을 입고 있었죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 131.21,
      "end": 132.47,
      "text": "Okay"
    },
    {
      "start": 132.47,
      "end": 134.05,
      "text": "Oh, William이 근데"
    },
    {
      "start": 134.05,
      "end": 136.89,
      "text": "어떤 인터뷰에서 중요한 말을 했다면서요"
    },
    {
      "start": 136.89,
      "end": 137.77,
      "text": "Oh, yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 137.77,
      "end": 140.29,
      "text": "Actually, she was talking about"
    },
    {
      "start": 140.29,
      "end": 141.17,
      "text": "her character"
    },
    {
      "start": 141.17,
      "end": 142.79,
      "text": "Her life in India"
    },
    {
      "start": 142.79,
      "end": 144.27,
      "text": "And she said"
    },
    {
      "start": 144.27,
      "end": 145.83,
      "text": "I thought of her as somebody"
    },
    {
      "start": 145.83,
      "end": 147.57,
      "text": "who used to burn very hot"
    },
    {
      "start": 147.57,
      "end": 150.41,
      "text": "and whose fire had to be extinguished"
    },
    {
      "start": 150.41,
      "end": 152.49,
      "text": "So, a very passionate lady"
    },
    {
      "start": 152.49,
      "end": 155.29,
      "text": "And that only a place like India"
    },
    {
      "start": 155.29,
      "end": 157.51,
      "text": "with all its sights and smells and sounds"
    },
    {
      "start": 157.51,
      "end": 159.65,
      "text": "can calm a person like this"
    },
    {
      "start": 159.65,
      "end": 161.55,
      "text": "Aha, now I understand"
    },
    {
      "start": 161.55,
      "end": 163.09,
      "text": "why she was always"
    },
    {
      "start": 163.09,
      "end": 164.91,
      "text": "you know, wearing the red cape"
    },
    {
      "start": 164.91,
      "end": 167.37,
      "text": "Yeah, she's very passionate"
    },
    {
      "start": 167.37,
      "end": 169.21,
      "text": "And India"
    },
    {
      "start": 169.21,
      "end": 170.57,
      "text": "with all its sights and sounds"
    },
    {
      "start": 170.57,
      "end": 171.63,
      "text": "Have you ever been to India?"
    },
    {
      "start": 172.79,
      "end": 173.99,
      "text": "인도는 아니고 네팔"
    },
    {
      "start": 173.99,
      "end": 174.63,
      "text": "Okay"
    },
    {
      "start": 174.63,
      "end": 175.41,
      "text": "You went to Nepal"
    },
    {
      "start": 175.41,
      "end": 176.55,
      "text": "Very similar to India"
    },
    {
      "start": 176.55,
      "end": 177.93,
      "text": "I went to India once"
    },
    {
      "start": 177.93,
      "end": 178.77,
      "text": "when my"
    },
    {
      "start": 178.77,
      "end": 180.13,
      "text": "after I got married"
    },
    {
      "start": 180.13,
      "end": 181.63,
      "text": "to a place called Chennai"
    },
    {
      "start": 181.63,
      "end": 182.21,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 182.21,
      "end": 183.65,
      "text": "And it is so different"
    },
    {
      "start": 183.65,
      "end": 185.09,
      "text": "than any place I'd ever been"
    },
    {
      "start": 185.09,
      "end": 187.53,
      "text": "So many different sights, sounds, foods"
    },
    {
      "start": 187.53,
      "end": 190.31,
      "text": "It was a completely new experience"
    },
    {
      "start": 190.31,
      "end": 192.05,
      "text": "So, I understand what she's saying"
    },
    {
      "start": 192.05,
      "end": 194.33,
      "text": "It can really calm someone down"
    },
    {
      "start": 194.33,
      "end": 195.95,
      "text": "because it's kind of overwhelming"
    },
    {
      "start": 195.95,
      "end": 197.49,
      "text": "if you're a foreigner"
    },
    {
      "start": 197.49,
      "end": 197.63,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 197.63,
      "end": 197.99,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 197.99,
      "end": 198.19,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 198.19,
      "end": 199.97,
      "text": "내 마음이 복잡한 상황에"
    },
    {
      "start": 199.97,
      "end": 201.81,
      "text": "만약에 인도나 네팔을 가게 되면"
    },
    {
      "start": 201.81,
      "end": 204.15,
      "text": "주변이 너무 복잡하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 204.15,
      "end": 206.75,
      "text": "막 경적 소리도 계속 쉬지 않고 나고"
    },
    {
      "start": 206.75,
      "end": 207.51,
      "text": "막 이러다 보니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 207.51,
      "end": 210.63,
      "text": "정신을 나한테 쓸 겨를이 없는 거죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 210.63,
      "end": 211.13,
      "text": "Yes"
    },
    {
      "start": 211.13,
      "end": 212.23,
      "text": "Oh, what's this?"
    },
    {
      "start": 212.29,
      "end": 212.69,
      "text": "Oh, it's new"
    },
    {
      "start": 212.69,
      "end": 213.41,
      "text": "Oh, that's new too"
    },
    {
      "start": 213.41,
      "end": 213.71,
      "text": "That's right"
    },
    {
      "start": 213.71,
      "end": 215.25,
      "text": "Everything's new"
    },
    {
      "start": 215.25,
      "end": 218.39,
      "text": "어쨌든, 이자베이 왜 인도에 가서 살았는지도"
    },
    {
      "start": 218.39,
      "end": 220.27,
      "text": "이해가 되는 내용이었습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 220.27,
      "end": 222.35,
      "text": "먼저 오늘 장면 듣고 올게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 222.35,
      "end": 224.15,
      "text": "Why are you doing this?"
    },
    {
      "start": 224.61,
      "end": 225.47,
      "text": "Because I want to"
    },
    {
      "start": 225.47,
      "end": 227.03,
      "text": "Why can't you just be grateful?"
    },
    {
      "start": 227.53,
      "end": 230.31,
      "text": "Because I know when things seem too good to be true"
    },
    {
      "start": 230.31,
      "end": 232.27,
      "text": "I think the only thing you need to know"
    },
    {
      "start": 232.27,
      "end": 233.31,
      "text": "is what to do with the money"
    },
    {
      "start": 233.31,
      "end": 234.11,
      "text": "Honestly"
    },
    {
      "start": 234.11,
      "end": 235.23,
      "text": "So it's a good day"
    },
    {
      "start": 235.23,
      "end": 236.73,
      "text": "It's a good day for both of us"
    },
    {
      "start": 236.73,
      "end": 239.57,
      "text": "This is strange to see Lasker again"
    },
    {
      "start": 239.57,
      "end": 241.13,
      "text": "You know, I mean"
    },
    {
      "start": 241.13,
      "end": 242.19,
      "text": "Does he look different now?"
    },
    {
      "start": 243.63,
      "end": 245.29,
      "text": "I don't remember"
    },
    {
      "start": 245.29,
      "end": 249.8,
      "text": "지금 they were having a conversation at the restaurant"
    },
    {
      "start": 249.8,
      "end": 252.42,
      "text": "그러면서 중간에 만난"
    },
    {
      "start": 252.42,
      "end": 254.34,
      "text": "다른 기업에서 온 사람들한테"
    },
    {
      "start": 254.34,
      "end": 258.12,
      "text": "I'm about to donate a small fortune to the orphanage"
    },
    {
      "start": 258.12,
      "end": 260.0,
      "text": "라고 했었던 게 저는 기억이 나요"
    },
    {
      "start": 260.0,
      "end": 261.94,
      "text": "Yeah, a small fortune"
    },
    {
      "start": 261.94,
      "end": 263.18,
      "text": "A lot of money"
    },
    {
      "start": 263.18,
      "end": 263.96,
      "text": "그러니까요"
    },
    {
      "start": 263.96,
      "end": 265.44,
      "text": "She keeps raising the money too"
    },
    {
      "start": 265.44,
      "end": 269.08,
      "text": "한 2천만 달러 기부를 할 거라고 얘기를 했었는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 269.08,
      "end": 269.68,
      "text": "여기서는"
    },
    {
      "start": 269.68,
      "end": 271.96,
      "text": "A small fortune이라고 표현들을 해가지고"
    },
    {
      "start": 271.96,
      "end": 273.76,
      "text": "화들짝 놀랐던 기억이 납니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 273.76,
      "end": 275.16,
      "text": "It sounds like a big fortune"
    },
    {
      "start": 275.16,
      "end": 275.64,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 275.64,
      "end": 277.54,
      "text": "She started with 2 million dollars"
    },
    {
      "start": 277.54,
      "end": 278.46,
      "text": "about 20억"
    },
    {
      "start": 278.46,
      "end": 280.76,
      "text": "and now it's at 20 million"
    },
    {
      "start": 280.76,
      "end": 282.48,
      "text": "That's a big difference"
    },
    {
      "start": 282.48,
      "end": 285.16,
      "text": "Times 10"
    },
    {
      "start": 285.16,
      "end": 286.94,
      "text": "But as we know"
    },
    {
      "start": 286.94,
      "end": 287.56,
      "text": "Isabel"
    },
    {
      "start": 287.56,
      "end": 289.5,
      "text": "She's not easily persuaded"
    },
    {
      "start": 289.5,
      "end": 290.26,
      "text": "Yeah, that's right"
    },
    {
      "start": 290.26,
      "end": 291.68,
      "text": "And she has her doubts"
    },
    {
      "start": 291.68,
      "end": 293.48,
      "text": "Why does she keep"
    },
    {
      "start": 293.48,
      "end": 294.98,
      "text": "wanting to give me more money?"
    },
    {
      "start": 295.12,
      "end": 295.4,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 295.4,
      "end": 296.9,
      "text": "되게 의아했을 것 같아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 296.9,
      "end": 298.2,
      "text": "왜 그렇게 많은 돈을"
    },
    {
      "start": 298.2,
      "end": 299.54,
      "text": "나에게 자꾸 주려고 하는 거지?"
    },
    {
      "start": 300.06,
      "end": 301.72,
      "text": "기부를 왜 자꾸 하려고 하는 거지?"
    },
    {
      "start": 302.14,
      "end": 304.04,
      "text": "라고 의심이 들 수도 있을 것 같습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 304.04,
      "end": 306.02,
      "text": "Yeah, like if you're just walking down the street"
    },
    {
      "start": 306.02,
      "end": 306.72,
      "text": "and someone said"
    },
    {
      "start": 306.72,
      "end": 308.2,
